    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, slice the<strong> cherry tomatoes </strong>in half</p><p>Strip the <strong>mint leaves</strong> from the stems and chop them roughly</p><p>Chop the <strong>coriander </strong>roughly, including the stalks</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
